= SSL Configuration =

This page allows setting up the SSL Settings and also displays the details of the current SSL configuration. Note, that incorrect or incomplete setup on this page can make the system inaccessible. Therefore, please backup your settings before you proceed. A restart is required before all settings take effect.

See also the full [[Help:SSL_HowTo| tutorial]] or [[Help:Installation#Installing_a_Custom_HTTPS_Certificate| here]] for further details (e.g, for information on how to prepare a keystore).

{{#ifexpr: {{#sparql: Java:com.fluidops.iwb.util.SSLSetup#isTrustStoreUp2Date}} | 
  <!-- up 2 date -->
 | <span style="color: red;">Your API truststore seems to be out-of-date and does not contain the latest root certificates. Please either use the bundled original ''fluidops.ca'' trust-store or follow the instructions [[Help:SSL_HowTo| here]] to create/upgrade your custom trust store.</span>
}}

