== Enabled SSL Protocols ==

The following table lists the enabled SSL protocols. 

In {{PRODUCT}} we change the default configuration of the JRE: By default the ''SSLv3'' protocol is disabled in newer Java versions (see [http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/topics/security/poodlecve-2014-3566-2339408.html here] for details). Since certain infrastructure systems require this protocol for their communication, in {{PRODUCT}} we modify the security manager configuration using the ''etc/java.security'' file (and particularly, the ''jdk.tls.disabledAlgorithms'' setting).

{{#widget: TableResult | 
 query = 'Java:com.fluidops.iwb.util.SSLSetup#getEnabledSSLProtocols'
 | columnConfiguration = {{ 
      {{ variableName = 'protocols'
       | displayName = 'Enabled Protocols'
      }} }}
}}

